      "writtenOn": "2017-10-05T23:31:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am not sure our use StatusTime will not break because of we have different ways of computing time. For a single builder, the method of StatusTime computation should be always the same. Consider\n\nBuild1: creation time\u003d1\nbuild2: commit time\u003d20\nbuild3: creation time \u003d 3\n\nbuild3 is ignored\n\nI will review the rest of this file when we resolve this comment",
