      "writtenOn": "2017-10-05T23:31:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "luci-notify used only for continuous builds in practice, right?\nhow about dropping this case.\nThis way the status time comparison code will stay correct AND status time will be computed based on commit order (what we care about), as opposed to build creation order",
      "revId": "fe85a23186f29b292381b93f5b788eb6d34d67a1",
