        "id": 1154295
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-10-06T02:38:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "OK so my decision to do this was based on the assumption that there would in-fact be builders that had no repository associated with them on the Fuchsia side. Notably, the fuchsia builders work this way. However, after talking with others, we\u0027ve determined that if we really need this case we\u0027ll make superprojects, so I\u0027m going to drop all this.",
      "parentUuid": "2a272926_b1446b87",
      "revId": "fe85a23186f29b292381b93f5b788eb6d34d67a1",
